Initialize variables
Roll one dice 6 million times and count it
display a tabular report
===
Initialize the arraySize to a constant value of 7.
Initialize the array of counts to all zeros. This array is of type unsigned int
Initialize a random engine, using time as a seed
Initialze a uniform integer distribution over interval 1 to 6.

Initialze a counter to 1
while the counter is less than or equal to 6 million
  increment the element number corresponding to the face value of the dice
  increment the counter

display the header consisting of "Face"  and "Frequency"
Initialize a counter to 1
while the counter is less than the array size
  display the counter number (equivalent to face value), padded 4
  display the count of the face number, padded 13
  goto a new line
